{"tid":1518924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【推上去】聽日 請你地準備好同警犬硬碰硬既覺悟","createTime":"2019-08-30T11:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:24:31.000Z","uid":258797,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1078755b1f5c7e15c523728ae511323d4a428afa","tid":1518924,"uid":258797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"回想番 <br />\n點解612可以壓制住班狗打<br />\n727元朗又可以㩒住班狗打 <br />\n主要原因係因為兩個字<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心態</span></span><br />\n<br />\n612我地個個都有曬決心要阻止開會<br />\n成個風氣都係預左拎條命嚟搏 有啲人甚至準備好曬犧牲<br />\n<br />\n727我地全部都預左入去元朗打班鄉黑 <br />\n雖然最後變左打狗 但係我地一早就有曬開戰既覺悟 所以先可以壓制到佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係想贏既 全部人都同我有呢個硬碰硬既覺悟<br />\n如果唔係 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">只會不斷重演 退後 被人拉既劇本</span><br />\n<br />\n有時唔係想要特登搞到變END GAME <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而係有END GAME既心態 我地先會贏</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日見<br />\n<br />\n幫我推上去"},{"pid":"8673ef6265da0a6cdac7d399a925e1e1f96fc09b","tid":1518924,"uid":258797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:44:09.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"229c62c4f2a27ec4f561230ea1b8ade4b42be1dc","tid":1518924,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831無大台 自行選地點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUis3u7Zzj2Sx3DhCMr